{"tid":494852,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"4 日 3 夜新北海線台中高雄單車鐵道之旅","createTime":"2017-12-10T06:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T11:41:36.000Z","uid":33484,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc457130008c4ec5c248a2e230e5f443dd92c8c","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"又係我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想重溫先前嘅韓國之旅可以去呢度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/482370/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/482370/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n話說都年幾兩年冇去過台灣<br />\n有啲地方甚至闊別幾年<br />\n而且都幾掛住啲美食<br />\n趁有時間去個短 trip<br />\n行程睇標題已經有晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前戲<br />\n<br />\n機票<br />\n桃園入高雄走<br />\nskyscanner 見到最平竟然係因航 <br />\n$1200 左右有<br />\n不過係經間叫 <a href=\"http://via.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvia.com&d=ePCWnjtSfoUi8ES%2FkCpDSzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5fe02f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">via.com</a> 嘅買<br />\ngoogle 過間嘢好似冇伏<br />\n買咗之後等咗日幾兩日就收到機票確認信<br />\n順利上機<br />\n<br />\n錢<br />\n都係開海外算<br />\n撳咗 TWD5000<br />\n<br />\n去馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8a545c79ef186140f0d801a422dff99b15237d","tid":494852,"uid":41441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"我想20-27飛台北，但機票成2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3b05061b1c199100a721796791bca211461b0e","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"對坐開廉航嘅窮撚<br />\n有飛機餐食真係覺得好奢侈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LrUOLpPl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLrUOLpPl.jpg&h=dd7acbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經認唔出係桃園機場<br />\n上次嚟仲裝修緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i6BYc7al.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi6BYc7al.jpg&h=443468dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本之行程重點之一<br />\n<del>陶喆</del>桃捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經唔記得呢條線搞咗幾耐<br />\n只記得係咁測試再測試<br />\n通車日期係咁褪<br />\n<br />\n由機場去台北車站<br />\n約 40 分鐘收你 TWD160<br />\n國光客運就 55 分鐘 TWD125<br />\n其實差別真係唔大<br />\n<br />\n分直通車同普通車<br />\n作為鐵膠當然坐慢車<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c5lugwMl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc5lugwMl.jpg&h=415fe4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大部份車站都係高架式<br />\n係頭尾幾個站先喺地底<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NrviE6ml.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNrviE6ml.jpg&h=bbd34db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車身內外用紫白做主色<br />\n望落舒服<br />\n至於車廂外型就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mNB77KWl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmNB77KWl.jpg&h=af246d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直通車內籠<br />\n好似香港機鐵咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tkugDShl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtkugDShl.jpg&h=30b3b831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tC79Hnul.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtC79Hnul.jpg&h=0c8d4d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿線風景<br />\n近桃園市區嘅就新市鎮咁款<br />\n好多新落成或者起緊嘅樓<br />\n郊區嘅就好似西鐵穿過錦上路咁<br />\n有山有水有田<br />\n不過係十倍計<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XCznXexl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXCznXexl.jpg&h=d4a64003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jd8G0ZFl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjd8G0ZFl.jpg&h=d57bf25a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6MIHWTl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW6MIHWTl.jpg&h=5e7460cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桃捷台北車站<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gm53Yqll.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fgm53Yqll.jpg&h=6cb8fd44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DReTJ2el.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDReTJ2el.jpg&h=b3384325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VylfdGul.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVylfdGul.jpg&h=ca4d24c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06f2fbc8f493226bdc7acbbd8da1b668753d4a08","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想20-27飛台北，但機票成2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖誕喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d094457dbdfa9c20df7ed361acd79a192c403308","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"由於喺機場坐返去環北<br />\n再去返台北車站<br />\n所以都坐咗成兩個幾鐘<br />\n去到台北車站即刻食返個台鐵便當醫肚<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DOtO6iXl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDOtO6iXl.jpg&h=1cd9a3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認唔認到係咩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gobQw0fl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgobQw0fl.jpg&h=0dfab886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天色未免太好<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kNAibQ9l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkNAibQ9l.jpg&h=489a666d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟到本次行程重點之二<br />\n先賣個關子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講以為去咗日本<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lwXbl4ll.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlwXbl4ll.jpg&h=c9663ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PB0zPFul.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPB0zPFul.jpg&h=e10af23d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當自己去咗海芝浦<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0yL3xRLl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0yL3xRLl.jpg&h=5ad6b910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開估<br />\n位於新北市瑞芳區<br />\n深澳線八斗子車站<br />\n有「北台灣多良車站」美譽咁話<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wAfdRfNl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwAfdRfNl.jpg&h=79bcd432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NciFUtwl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNciFUtwl.jpg&h=b4eb7c74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"287963788fd017a10cdc8d26382497e6887e8489","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"預備行程嗰時就睇下呢區有咩好行啦<br />\n發現有唔少自然景點<br />\n不過用腳行就辛苦得滯<br />\n又畀我搵到呢邊有間叫 obike 嘅單車租<br />\n咁就掂晒啦<br />\n<br />\n與事實相乎<br />\n可惜塊牌個位唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6uPodvIl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6uPodvIl.jpg&h=edd8448a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲景真係望一世都唔會厭<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/x0tqh5Bl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fx0tqh5Bl.jpg&h=64661126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由八斗子車站出發<br />\n沿海向北踩<br />\n會經過潮境公園同環保復育公園<br />\n擺放咗好多藝術品喺度<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5ZHtRD1l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5ZHtRD1l.jpg&h=13796c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HtoMm61l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHtoMm61l.jpg&h=e17742b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sXqYCmjl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsXqYCmjl.jpg&h=3053d646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後向海科館方向<br />\n沿八斗路北行<br />\n上望幽谷觀海平台<br />\n不過呢條係山路<br />\n唔好諗住可以踩車上到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TBDzQAOl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTBDzQAOl.jpg&h=89760fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q5tNFLxl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq5tNFLxl.jpg&h=95a3819e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落返山都接近黃昏<br />\n由於搵唔到有專用位泊<br />\n就咁放低架車就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有樣好笑嘢<br />\n當初租呢架車係先單佢個 app<br />\n再用 fb login<br />\n咩個人資料 (空帳戶) 同信用卡資料都冇畀<br />\n到最後我都唔明佢點收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MREaOWIl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMREaOWIl.jpg&h=d8e24c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於深澳線車極疏<br />\n計啱時間搭公車返瑞芳再返台北<br />\n<br />\n終於食到久違嘅蚵仔煎同魯肉飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/F4y3YV6l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FF4y3YV6l.jpg&h=b911d7fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n住就 <a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=ePCWnjtSfoUi8ES%2FkCpDSzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=def2869f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">booking.com</a> 搵 backpacker hostel<br />\n叫巴客來青年旅館<br />\n喺松山車站附近<br />\n初頭以為大伏<br />\n因為要喺幢望落好霉嘅大廈上樓<br />\n點知係極豪裝同新淨<br />\n非常滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4fMzXdhl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4fMzXdhl.jpg&h=acbcae0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一日完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa9a52f4574c6da70712644ba4e6e1211578558","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"第二日<br />\n<br />\n好明顯第二日開始就係海線遊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次南下一定係坐山線<br />\n今次就趁機坐海線<br />\n擁抱一下台灣西部海岸<br />\n順道睇下幾個有名嘅木造車站<br />\n<br />\n晨早出門<br />\n早餐都係便利店搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ud7jaNil.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fud7jaNil.jpg&h=ae42cfaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐五點幾車去竹南轉海線<br />\n咁就周圍影下<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pHniZcVl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpHniZcVl.jpg&h=c3b53c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UrDG08al.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUrDG08al.jpg&h=c0e81994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UwQyUWRl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUwQyUWRl.jpg&h=06a81eba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人稱海線五寶嘅五個木造車站<br />\n分別係談文、大山、新埔、日南、追分<br />\n係台灣日治時期建成嘅日式車站<br />\n由於海線班次基本上成個幾鐘先一班<br />\n時間關係都冇喺所有站落晒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n談文<br />\n一落車就陣陣清新嘅牛屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GT2wrfZl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGT2wrfZl.jpg&h=920fd9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bmZFieOl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbmZFieOl.jpg&h=77066ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kaU3PoAl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkaU3PoAl.jpg&h=3cdff5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/55Mb1N1l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F55Mb1N1l.jpg&h=e92ecc2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zahEH3Tl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzahEH3Tl.jpg&h=1b2e5c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大山<br />\n時間關係就咁望一眼算<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FrEF79vl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFrEF79vl.jpg&h=dd9c284d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住喺白沙屯落車<br />\n原因係上網搵到有單車租<br />\n可以欣賞下西部海岸<br />\n順便去埋新埔車站<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3CBVamUl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3CBVamUl.jpg&h=347d8d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rp1s4gll.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRp1s4gll.jpg&h=03fa59df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白沙屯海堤<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1omc21Ql.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1omc21Ql.jpg&h=7c768660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mFep0lel.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmFep0lel.jpg&h=92f685a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/r0jg6bOl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr0jg6bOl.jpg&h=2ee20202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台鐵車廂餐廳<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/H3bnSovl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FH3bnSovl.jpg&h=686ed5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然只係一個站<br />\n搭鐵就 3 分鐘<br />\nhea 踩都要成 9 個字<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f11IzNXl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff11IzNXl.jpg&h=2322dea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nmzHhxKl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnmzHhxKl.jpg&h=268edb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新埔車站<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iySEGJKl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiySEGJKl.jpg&h=11b70eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1B87jhLl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1B87jhLl.jpg&h=f7c35f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回程時見到有好多車手補給<br />\n好熱血<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B1KUoonl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FB1KUoonl.jpg&h=8a3786bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日南車站<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8r1vQXNl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8r1vQXNl.jpg&h=4b7a9b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hBe1y6el.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhBe1y6el.jpg&h=10287e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0t2t6Hgl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0t2t6Hgl.jpg&h=5dd3d8b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8967e19ad587338028ae518d77f378ff34cbbd9a","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"到彰化已經係點半<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i1f9sC0l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi1f9sC0l.jpg&h=4e113b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uYMGc0Al.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuYMGc0Al.jpg&h=3d9e17a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到個名咁得意<br />\n即管試下<br />\n又幾好食喎<br />\n原來貓鼠係講緊老闆喺鋪頭左穿右插上菜嘅身手敏捷如鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GGWnAC6l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGGWnAC6l.jpg&h=a81ae90d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RDOrTzil.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRDOrTzil.jpg&h=a2247704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食碗咁嘅麵當然唔夠飽<br />\n隔離整多碗芋圓冰<br />\n汲取經驗<br />\n特登叫老闆娘少冰<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FoxB46Ql.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFoxB46Ql.jpg&h=c1fe00b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VFAyJOgl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVFAyJOgl.jpg&h=f8da0357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一站<br />\n扇形車廠<br />\n多人到唔想影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/T5f0AYVl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FT5f0AYVl.jpg&h=954e46ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tu5kXbTl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ftu5kXbTl.jpg&h=cec5813b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住到新烏日車站<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LNgUOUQl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLNgUOUQl.jpg&h=fabef952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5QfT9fZl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5QfT9fZl.jpg&h=eb8316b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉巴士嚟到彩虹眷村<br />\n港人 S 線熱門打卡地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廣受世界各地媒體採訪就不在話下<br />\n但真係睇介紹先知<br />\n彩虹爺爺竟然由香港嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AySqbhll.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAySqbhll.jpg&h=1b27eec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WycTskfl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWycTskfl.jpg&h=eb35ce25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8foHdhgl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8foHdhgl.jpg&h=258ca74f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bae0fdf5895f9a9bd0387eee4e6144925d10239","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"由於時間關係<br />\nskip 咗追分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台中車站<br />\n上次嚟新站都未開始起<br />\n數年後一切俱往矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HZrycQSl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHZrycQSl.jpg&h=1054391a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/33utATIl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F33utATIl.jpg&h=089c072a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到而家先知宮原眼科係賣糖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FusUJNc.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFusUJNc.jpg%3F1&h=1c3e5b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jKv3Quh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjKv3Quh.jpg&h=0bba4dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柳川<br />\n好似度度都有治河工程咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7n2AFar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7n2AFar.jpg&h=7914cd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5Q2uOtN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5Q2uOtN.jpg&h=e8e063a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動漫彩繪巷<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eD9YtXy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeD9YtXy.jpg&h=e00956f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/stKlRLc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FstKlRLc.jpg&h=b658793b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K0Zi7a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK0Zi7a4.jpg&h=ae9a854a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚餐<br />\n杯水果茶真係好多生果喺裡面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐵板麵夠晒鑊氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OR6hIjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOR6hIjO.jpg&h=aea03d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二日完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5157d63dc7d8e2d4a0ee24f019dea858f41729b3","tid":494852,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"正，我上次都3日2夜台灣鐵道遊，不過就台北經宜蘭花蓮台東去高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2150a20d26d6b0532bacfce2662cb47398e28f2","tid":494852,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"單車在哪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重以為你環島個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debaf07825369bac5c465d1b01c3244522da75ab","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正，我上次都3日2夜台灣鐵道遊，不過就台北經宜蘭花蓮台東去高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋感覺東部慢好多<br />\n又成日入隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a7d157bc486a8226499ab9b8d248a2dc2957fd","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單車在哪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重以為你環島個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我每日都有貼架單車出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4 日邊可能環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28baad6819d5c5fb79d5988aeb93bfdf2924bbf2","tid":494852,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正，我上次都3日2夜台灣鐵道遊，不過就台北經宜蘭花蓮台東去高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋感覺東部慢好多<br />\n又成日入隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東部幹線好多位重係單線，慢係好正常<br />\n之前即日來回高雄花蓮重要大delay，差d miss尾班車返高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d62abda0e47d051ae38dc0830536ffe5f5d691","tid":494852,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>單車在哪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重以為你環島個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我每日都有貼架單車出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4 日邊可能環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家明哂"},{"pid":"c78c616e77dd604cfa4479ff0986b395cae0b004","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"第 3 日<br />\n<br />\n尾站嚟到高雄<br />\n除咗因為喺呢度返香港<br />\n亦因為已經闊別高雄 5 年 (好似係)<br />\n想睇下有咩唔同咗<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住就咁嘟悠遊卡入閘<br />\n但諗諗下<br />\n唔係喎<br />\n落高雄呢班對號車嚟<br />\n冇位坐咪企到腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻去 counter 買返張飛先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">因為幾年前真係由台中企到落高雄<br />\n自強快極都兩個鐘</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣永遠都係用黑熊做吉祥物<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OMVxKqrl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOMVxKqrl.jpg&h=86c03602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高雄車站<br />\n高雄搞緊高雄市區鐵路地下化<br />\n沿線車站都大整緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ce3RuTLl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCe3RuTLl.jpg&h=e9491012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yuFRbgrl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyuFRbgrl.jpg&h=6172cc1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台鐵武士<br />\n<em><strong>台鐵機器人是台灣鐵路管理局台北機廠利用報廢的柴電機車引擎零件所做的創意作品</strong></em><br />\n喺台北、台中車站同扇形車庫都見到有<br />\n如果出模型應該幾受歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hpE7ri8l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhpE7ri8l.jpg&h=eef0ece0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首站<br />\n當然係搭新鮮出爐嘅輕軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成套嘢感覺同愛丁堡電車一樣<br />\n最白痴係冇得用悠遊卡<br />\n聽聞係發卡公司間利益問題所致<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UtIxIH6l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUtIxIH6l.jpg&h=7cae5e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WEdragxl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWEdragxl.jpg&h=68cd679b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1M4V0P3l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1M4V0P3l.jpg&h=46353935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KXUh2sYl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKXUh2sYl.jpg&h=de412067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K74T2c2l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK74T2c2l.jpg&h=3fd6fd77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現階段高雄輕軌得一條線<br />\n沿住碼頭咁行<br />\n一路搭就去到駁二啦<br />\n印象中幾年前嘅駁二都未有規模<br />\n幾年後已經有眾多唔同類型展館<br />\n草地亦已經成為輕軌總站同市民休憩之地<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tYakLr5l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtYakLr5l.jpg&h=92fe966f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AHKPG4ml.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAHKPG4ml.jpg&h=03f6f83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tTzeGppl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtTzeGppl.jpg&h=2c2a3d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KNKzjJJl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKNKzjJJl.jpg&h=2d256593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yz7oBV9l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fyz7oBV9l.jpg&h=8768110b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XaoCfGwl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXaoCfGwl.jpg&h=39174f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3Xzx0WMl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3Xzx0WMl.jpg&h=60744c66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39deb81d92a865391537a67b2dbd20adc59713cb","tid":494852,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正，我上次都3日2夜台灣鐵道遊，不過就台北經宜蘭花蓮台東去高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋感覺東部慢好多<br /